trans-unit.source: Represents a <xref uid="langword_csharp_<caches>" name="<caches>" href=""></xref> element in a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en <xref uid="langword_csharp_<caches>" name="<caches>" href=""> </xref> element i en konfigurasjonsfil.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The `<caches>` element configures the caching services for WIF.
trans-unit.target: Den `<caches>` elementet konfigurerer hurtigbufring-tjenester i WIF.

trans-unit.source: It registers the type of session security token cache and the type of token replay cache to use.
trans-unit.target: Det registrerer av token hurtigbuffer for sikkerhet og hva slags token spill hurtigbufferen for å bruke.

trans-unit.source: It can be specified at the service level under the `<identityConfiguration>` element or on a security token handler collection under the `<securityTokenHandlerConfiguration>` element.
trans-unit.target: Det kan angis på tjenestenivå under den `<identityConfiguration>` element eller på en sikkerhet token behandlingsprogrammet samling under den `<securityTokenHandlerConfiguration>` elementet.

trans-unit.source: The `Caches` property of the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.IdentityConfigurationElement> class and of the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.SecurityTokenHandlerConfigurationElement> class is an instance of IdentityModelCachesElement.
trans-unit.target: Den `Caches` -egenskapen for den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.IdentityConfigurationElement>klassen av den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.SecurityTokenHandlerConfigurationElement>klassen er en forekomst av IdentityModelCachesElement.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.SecurityTokenHandlerConfigurationElement> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.IdentityConfigurationElement>

trans-unit.source: After the configuration file has been read, the configured caches are represented by the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.IdentityModelCaches> class.
trans-unit.target: Når konfigurasjonsfilen er lest, representeres konfigurert hurtigbufrer av <xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.IdentityModelCaches>klasse.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.IdentityModelCaches>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Configuration.IdentityModelCachesElement"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Configuration.IdentityModelCachesElement"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether this element has been configured.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om dette elementet har blitt konfigurert.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the element has been configured; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis elementet har blitt konfigurert. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som skal legges til.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref:System.Type> of the session token cache.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den <xref:System.Type>økten token-hurtigbufferen.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: This property is optional.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er valgfrie.

trans-unit.source: It corresponds to a `<sessionSecurityTokenCache>` element specified under the `<caches>`.
trans-unit.target: Det samsvarer med en `<sessionSecurityTokenCache>` element som er angitt under den `<caches>`.

trans-unit.source: It specifies the type of the cache to use to store session security tokens.
trans-unit.target: Den angir hurtigbufferen for å bruke til å lagre sikkerhetstokener for økten.

trans-unit.source: All session token caches must derive from <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenCache>
trans-unit.target: Alle økten token hurtigbuffere må være utledet fra<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenCache></xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenCache>

trans-unit.source: The type of the session token cache.
trans-unit.target: Typen for hurtigbufferen for økt-token.

trans-unit.source: The type must derive from [System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenCache](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Typen må være utledet fra [System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SessionSecurityTokenCache](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref:System.Type> of the token replay cache.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den <xref:System.Type>spille hurtigbufferen for tokenet.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: This property is optional.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er valgfrie.

trans-unit.source: It corresponds to an `<tokenReplayCache>` element specified under the `<caches>` element.
trans-unit.target: Det samsvarer med en `<tokenReplayCache>` element som er angitt under den `<caches>` elementet.

trans-unit.source: It specifies the type of the cache to use to detect replayed tokens.
trans-unit.target: Den angir hurtigbufferen for å bruke til å oppdage gjentas tokener.

trans-unit.source: All replay caches must derive from <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.TokenReplayCache> Replay detection is enabled with the `<tokenReplayDetection>` element.
trans-unit.target: Alle spill hurtigbuffere må være utledet fra <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.TokenReplayCache>Spill gjenkjenning aktiveres med de `<tokenReplayDetection>` element.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.TokenReplayCache>

trans-unit.source: This element is represented by the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.TokenReplayDetectionElement> class.
trans-unit.target: Dette elementet er representert av <xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.TokenReplayDetectionElement>klasse.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Configuration.TokenReplayDetectionElement>

trans-unit.source: The type of the token replay cache.
trans-unit.target: Typen for hurtigbufferen token avspilling.

trans-unit.source: The type must derive from [System.IdentityModel.Tokens.TokenReplayCache](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Typen må være utledet fra [System.IdentityModel.Tokens.TokenReplayCache](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
